10. Re1 } ( { Black has mostly tried kicking back the knight, which makes a lot of sense since, as we have seen in the } 10...d6? { line, the knight on b5 is extremely dangerous for Black due to its potential to sacrifice itself on c7 or d6 at any moment. } ) 
