6. Qe2 } } { Another benefit of 6.Qe2 is that we invite Black to blunder with this tactical move. It's a tempting move for them since they target our knight on b5 and our queen on e2 and, in this way, hope to eliminate the pressure against c7. However... it's a big mistake! } 
