8. f3 } { It's nice to cover the g4-square to prevent ...Ng4 ideas. } O-O 
9. Qd2 $16  } { Setting up the queen-bishop battery and preparing to castle queenside. Our plan here will be the typical one of playing O-O-O and pushing our kingside pawns to launch an attack.

It's hard for Black to counter this since they don't have an active plan and with lots of our pieces on the queenside we are well-positioned to deal with any attack our opponents might try to conjure up. } *

