{ Welcome to a short selection of fun tactics in the Scotch! These positions are taken from the Scotch. Unlike the main tactics chapter, [/course/179653/23] which shows tactics that appear in our course repertoire, these tactics are a bit simpler and can arise from other variations of the Scotch that aren't a part of our specific repertoire. Some are quite easy, but others will be much more tricky!

If you don't want to, you can certainly skip this chapter, but if you'd like to do it, then it will be helpful for training pattern recognition. Good luck :) } 1. -- } *

